question:
What will be the output of the following C code?

```c
#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    int i = 5;
    do {
        printf("%d ", i);
        i--;
    } while (i > 0);
    return 0;
}
```

How many times will the following C loop execute?

```c
#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    int i = 10;
    do {
        printf("Hello");
    } while (i < 0);
    return 0;
}
```

What will be the output of this C code?

```c
#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    int i = 3;
    do {
        printf("%d ", i);
    } while (--i);
    return 0;
}
```
